After Joon123 allstar went offline. We present you part 2!
Better then ever before! :cool:
Owner,hoster,coder: Food left Co-owners: Wimstr, Trickshotter Mods: None
We are still improving the server, but are ready for u to come! Vps is coming soon, since we still update server is being home hosted by Food left.
Forums: joon123.makeaforum.net Our own client: http://uppit.com/liif1szrmarb/Custom_client.rar We got the following things:
-anti syi -anti null -dupes fixed -jad -kbd -shops -working jail system (yell block coming soon) -Checkip option -funpk and pkbox -teampk and pkzone -skilling place, different then on any other allstar! -ticket change and shop -different trains -barrows -xpmini and gsmini -unique home -dad boss!
And much more! Prepare for one of the best allstar server u will ever see! [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/30mabyt.jpg[/img]
